_sText:
"gg_death_arches"

This is a small sized symmetrical GG map. 
Buy Zones are included for Fight Yard style play too.

Each side has 2 black platforms that can elevate players up onto the arches.  Players can reach the top of every arch after they take the lift (screen shot 1).

Please download, comment and enjoy!

- 48 Spawns
- Cubemaps
- Optimized for better FPS
- Overview radar map
- Buy Zones
- Nav File
- Pakrat
- Custom Textures by Eric
